name: Blanco - CO (Cigar Obsession) Final Third - Toro
additionalNotes: David Blanco of Blanco Cigars has contributed his own widely-respected expertise towards creating a line of cigars that shows appreciation for Cigar Obsession and their mission to provide invaluable information to the smoking community.Â  The Final Third is a box-pressed medium-bodied cigar hailing from Nicaragua and manufactured by Plasencia.
